Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:57.42,Captions small,TL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord1.5\fad(700,0)\fs40\pos(746,592)}Alabastro do Reino da Areia
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.56,0:24:57.42,Main,Igaram,0,0,0,,O-O que...?!
